WordPress or Html is a common ask question amongst business owners and web developers. Unlike in the past, when the development of a simple website takes days if not months before launching.

In recent times, once an individual or business entity has decided to own a website. Depending on the complexities and functionalities of the website. A website can be fully developed and viewed across the globe in a couple of hours.

